{"tid":453908,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯涉以Facebook干預美大選","createTime":"2017-10-31T15:41:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-31T16:00:34.000Z","uid":153228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3104c6e3adbae93e443693df768d0f0ef54c2ebf","tid":453908,"uid":153228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T15:41:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%B6%89%E4%BB%A5facebook%E5%B9%B2%E9%A0%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8-%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E8%A2%AB%E6%8F%AD%E6%92%AD8%E8%90%AC%E5%88%86%E5%8C%96%E8%A8%8A%E6%81%AF-1-3%E5%84%84%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E7%9C%8B%E9%81%8E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E4%25BB%25A5facebook%25E5%25B9%25B2%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2581%25B8-%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258F%25AD%25E6%2592%25AD8%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%258C%2596%25E8%25A8%258A%25E6%2581%25AF-1-3%25E5%2584%2584%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2588%25B6%25E7%259C%258B%25E9%2581%258E%2F&d=SW0INPOEqdY4XwsDJT1F4%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=d504595c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E4%25BB%25A5facebook%25E5%25B9%25B2%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2581%25B8-%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258F%25AD%25E6%2592%25AD8%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%258C%2596%25E8%25A8%258A%25E6%2581%25AF-1-3%25E5%2584%2584%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2588%25B6%25E7%259C%258B%25E9%2581%258E%2F&h=11e9e8ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%B6%89%E4%BB%A5facebook%E5%B9%B2%E9%A0%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8-%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E8%A2%AB%E6%8F%AD%E6%92%AD8%E8%90%AC%E5%88%86%E5%8C%96%E8%A8%8A%E6%81%AF-1-3%E5%84%84%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E7%9C%8B%E9%81%8E/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/fb-1220copy_Xabko_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ffb-1220copy_Xabko_1200x0.png&h=e7e54719&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯試圖干預去年美國大選，美國參議院司法委員會（Senate Judiciary Committee）今明兩日舉行聽證會，facebook 等社交媒體機構將派員作供。facebook 率先披露大選期以來，由俄羅斯操縱機構發出的八萬個含分化內容的訊息，接觸到大約 1.26 億美國用戶，佔該國合資格選民人數一半。<br />\n<br />\n美國參議院司法委員會今明兩日舉行三場聽證會，詳細了解俄羅斯在社交網站的介入和參與，Facebook、Google 和Twitter 先後作供。《路透社》和《華盛頓郵報》分別引述消息人士指，facebook 將於今日提交書面證供。<br />\n<br />\n據該消息人士透露，證供內容指與俄羅斯克里姆林宮有聯繫的機構「互聯網研究社」（Internet Research Agency）在 facebook 開設 120 個專頁，並於 2015 年 1 月至 2017 年 8 月期間發佈 8 萬則帖文。帖文內容涉及社會與政治分化，例如種族等議題。facebook 估計曾接觸相關訊息的美國用戶可能多達 1.26 億，即美國合資格選民人數的一半，預計資訊擴散範圍遠超於此。涉事機構曾於 2015 至 2017 年間，斥資十萬美元，購買超過 3 千個廣告。facebook 的總法律顧問 Colin Stretch 指，八萬則帖文佔整體訊息量不多，但危及平台建立社群的宗旨，違反網站的服務規定。"},{"pid":"f28e85ea66b2fa88d0f78e7a1f2e2ea0547c45fd","tid":453908,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T15:46:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b102d8cc4ef94475dcfd6f7576224408e0e405","tid":453908,"uid":22858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T15:48:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>鍵戰民族</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><ins>細字濃縮試用版</ins><br />\n經crosscheck多個post，確信五毛名單臚列如下：三色貓、法國佬巫斯義、群龍共舞、優美開始、JR、RedBaron、Gladiclus、D_Wade、dewi、newlife、bbchu、十卜Ching、侵B、吾系甘開心牙、返六日唔撚易、毛澤東<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<ins>證據一：五毛一見字眼空群而出</ins><br />\n連狗對五毛問題視而不見、置若罔聞，與全連登作對<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451623\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451623</a><br />\